== read_param  (key 34, down-camera X scale) ==

host → ctrl  (12 bytes)
01 00 00 00  22 00 00 00  00 00 00 00
^^                                       opcode = 0x01 read_param
   ^^                                    sequence = 0
      ^^                                 aux = 0
         ^^                              pad = 0
            ^^^^^^^^^^^                  key = 0x00000022 = 34   (downcam_scale_x)
                         ^^^^^^^^^^^     pad

ctrl → host  (12 bytes)
01 00 00 00  00 00 00 00  0C 01 00 00
^^                                       opcode_echo = 0x01
   ^^                                    sequence
      ^^                                 aux
         ^^                              pad
            ^^^^^^^^^^^                  reserved / echoed key area
                         ^^^^^^^^^^^     value = 0x0000010C = 268

DECODED:
    downcam_scale_x = 268 / 10000 = 0.0268 mm/pixel
